{"tid":1806721,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得嗌香港獨立係錯嘅手足","createTime":"2020-01-01T12:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T14:36:36.000Z","uid":195444,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb0e081fa80d7706efeb96dd928bd84fab26003","tid":1806721,"uid":195444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"你地學下藍絲啦，唔嗌都嗌咗，諗下點做到更好好過啦<br />\n成日話不割席，手足有冇做到呀？<br />\n定你地真係咁天真，覺得我地唔嗌口號，中國唔知我地想獨立？定真係覺得外國係為咗人權幫香港？嗌咗獨立就唔會幫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地真係想為件事好，應該兜下話中國太仆街，唔獨立唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比啲藉口外國，跟住自己香港加強宣傳，而唔係話唔得唔得，跟住割人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3124ba95a4dafd620ed30ceea94126e4afb8ab5b","tid":1806721,"uid":90499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:45:56.000Z","msg":"破窗論，要求香港獨立，就會應承五大訴求"},{"pid":"f176b7e02a5b57eb001935d3165ded20759d3a06","tid":1806721,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3124ba95a4dafd620ed30ceea94126e4afb8ab5b","tid":1806721,"uid":90499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:45:56.000Z","msg":"破窗論，要求香港獨立，就會應承五大訴求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"這就是獨立論"},{"pid":"05164acf39dc8afab79e9f8f1e0999e57587c47f","tid":1806721,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:49:58.000Z","msg":"點解共產黨乜鳩都話你攪港獨<br />\n明明五大無一個要求港獨佢都要話你港獨？共產黨就最想你地講港獨<br />\n咁就可以明正言順話保護國家 美國佬仲點用一國兩制來干預"},{"pid":"2b85d85d63e24b51774b527fd6725c3a6d0285a5","tid":1806721,"uid":235362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:56:14.000Z","msg":"唔獨立點廢除功能組別？<br />\n唔獨立又點做到五大訴求？<br />\n真係唯一出口呀&hellip;"},{"pid":"d08a2ccc2dc0604a505af7272bf339b4ca8768a0","tid":1806721,"uid":310883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"qu